[BAND PLAYING GEORGE GERSHWIN'S
"SUMMERTIME"]

1722
03:42:22,163 --> 03:42:23,623
[O'DONNELL CHUCKLES]

1723
03:42:26,459 --> 03:42:31,881
I must admit, this party
was a wonderful idea, Mr. Secretary.

1724
03:42:32,048 --> 03:42:35,760
