before the Committee in five days..."

1725
03:42:35,927 --> 03:42:38,304
but my conscience is clear.

1726
03:42:38,471 --> 03:42:42,350
"The most important people in New York
are my guests."

1727
03:42:42,517 --> 03:42:44,227
