to exercise your will.

1759
03:44:58,528 --> 03:44:59,946
I give up everything.

1760
03:45:02,657 --> 03:45:04,659
Twelve percent will be set aside
for your boy.

1761
03:45:05,493 --> 03:45:07,954
That way he can be assured...

1762
03:45:08,121 --> 03:45:10,707
