03:57:21,729 --> 03:57:25,816
When you've been betrayed by a friend,
you hit back.

1838
03:57:30,863 --> 03:57:32,698
Do it.

1839
03:57:54,678 --> 03:57:57,473
You see, Mr. Secretary...

1840
03:57:59,475 --> 03:58:01,560
